DAT
id=qid::label=str::text=lstr::
5702::$$$message_0053_0000_0000$$$::"Ah...!"[lr]::
5703::$$$message_0053_0000_0001$$$::I wake suddenly.[lr]::
5704::$$$message_0053_0000_0002$$$::I feel sick, and my entire body aches. Every time my heart beats, a sharp pain stabs my head.::
5705::$$$message_0053_0001_0000$$$::"What...happened?"[lr]::
5706::$$$message_0053_0001_0001$$$::My intense headache prevents me from remembering anything.[lr]::
5707::$$$message_0053_0001_0002$$$::My body is cold and stiff, likely because I've been sleeping in the hallway for a long time.[lr]::
5708::$$$message_0053_0001_0003$$$::The only thing I can figure out is that the chest area of my uniform is torn, and my blood stains the hall floor.::
5709::$$$message_0053_0002_0000$$$::"...Tch."[lr]::
5710::$$$message_0053_0002_0001$$$::My head feels hazy as I get up.[lr]::
5711::$$$message_0053_0002_0002$$$::The spot where I'd been lying looks like a murder scene.::
5712::$$$message_0053_0003_0000$$$::"Damn...seriously..."[lr]::
5713::$$$message_0053_0003_0001$$$::    Was my chest stabbed?::
5714::$$$message_0053_0004_0000$$$::"Hnn...haah...ng."[lr]::
5715::$$$message_0053_0004_0001$$$::I fight down a surge of nausea as I head into a nearby classroom.[lr]::
5716::$$$message_0053_0004_0002$$$::Staggering, I open a closet and pull out a rag and bucket.::
5717::$$$message_0053_0005_0000$$$::"Huh...what the hell am I doing...?"[lr]::
5718::$$$message_0053_0005_0001$$$::I'm still confused.[lr]::
5719::$$$message_0053_0005_0002$$$::I encountered something unbelievable, then it murdered me... But here I am, still trying to clean up after myself. How stupid can I be?::
5720::$$$message_0053_0006_0000$$$::"Hnn...hnn... Damn, it's not coming out."[lr]::
5721::$$$message_0053_0006_0001$$$::I wipe at the floor with a rag I found.[lr]::
5722::$$$message_0053_0006_0002$$$::I manage to wipe off the blood, despite the incredible weakness in my whole body, then gather up everything scattered around the floor and shove it in my pockets.[lr]::
5723::$$$message_0053_0006_0003$$$::This may be my way of hiding any evidence.[lr]::
5724::$$$message_0053_0006_0004$$$::I must be doing such stupid stuff because my head's all hazy.::
5725::$$$message_0053_0007_0000$$$::"Ah..."[lr]::
5726::$$$message_0053_0007_0001$$$::I put the rag and bucket away, and stagger out of the school like a zombie.[lr]::
5727::$$$message_0053_0007_0002$$$::My body heats up with every step I take.[lr]::
5728::$$$message_0053_0007_0003$$$::It's so cold outside, yet my body seems to be on fire.::
5729::$$$message_0053_0008_0000$$$::By the time I reach my house, the date has changed.[lr]::
5730::$$$message_0053_0008_0001$$$::There's nobody in the house.[lr]::
5731::$$$message_0053_0008_0002$$$::Sakura and even Fuji-nee left long ago.::
5732::$$$message_0053_0009_0000$$$::"...Ah... Gh... Hnn..."[lr]::
5733::$$$message_0053_0009_0001$$$::I collapse on the floor.[lr]::
5734::$$$message_0053_0009_0002$$$::Lying on the floor is what lets me finally calm down a bit.[lr]::
5735::$$$message_0053_0009_0003$$$::"..."[lr]::
5736::$$$message_0053_0009_0004$$$::I inhale deeply.::
5737::$$$message_0053_0010_0000$$$::My heart feels like it cracks every time my chest expands to draw in air.[lr]::
5738::$$$message_0053_0010_0001$$$::Actually, it's the opposite.[lr]::
5739::$$$message_0053_0010_0002$$$::It's not that my heart is cracking.[lr]::
5740::$$$message_0053_0010_0003$$$::The hole in my heart was just patched up, so expanding my chest opens the wound.::
5741::$$$message_0053_0011_0000$$$::"So I really was almost killed."[lr]::
5742::$$$message_0053_0011_0001$$$::That's also not true.[lr]::
5743::$$$message_0053_0011_0002$$$::I wasn't almost killed. I [font italic=true]was[font italic=false] killed.[lr]::
5744::$$$message_0053_0011_0003$$$::But someone saved me, and now I'm alive.::
5745::$$$message_0053_0012_0000$$$::"I wonder who it was. I would really like to thank them."[lr]::
5746::$$$message_0053_0012_0001$$$::If they were in the area it means they could be involved with the people fighting.[lr]::
5747::$$$message_0053_0012_0002$$$::But it still doesn't change the fact that they saved me. So I need to thank them properly one day.::
5748::$$$message_0053_0013_0000$$$::"Ah...ngh...!"[lr]::
5749::$$$message_0053_0013_0001$$$::The moment I drop my guard, the pain returns.[lr]::
5750::$$$message_0053_0013_0002$$$::At the same time, nausea strikes me.::
5751::$$$message_0053_0013_0003$$$::"Ah...ha...unnngh!"[lr]::
5752::$$$message_0053_0013_0004$$$::I sit up to hold the nausea at bay.[lr]::
5753::$$$message_0053_0013_0005$$$::"Ng...fu...hn..."[lr]::
5754::$$$message_0053_0013_0006$$$::I place my hand on my bare chest, where the uniform is torn.[lr]::
5755::$$$message_0053_0013_0007$$$::I might've been saved, but my chest was, as a matter of fact, pierced.::
5756::$$$message_0053_0013_0008$$$::That feeling.[lr]::
5757::$$$message_0053_0013_0009$$$::The agony of the spear tip piercing my chest isn't something I can easily forget.::
5758::$$$message_0053_0013_0010$$$::"Damn...I'm going to have nightmares about this for a while."[lr]::
5759::$$$message_0053_0013_0011$$$::When I close my eyes, I feel the spear thrust again.[lr]::
5760::$$$message_0053_0013_0012$$$::I try to shake that delusion off, and I make every effort to regain my composure.::
5761::$$$message_0053_0013_0013$$$::"Good, I'm calming down."[lr]::
5762::$$$message_0053_0013_0014$$$::This must be thanks to my nightly training.[lr]::
5763::$$$message_0053_0013_0015$$$::My thoughts clear as I take slow, deep breaths. The fever and nausea abate a bit.::
5764::$$$message_0053_0014_0000$$$::"So, about what happened..."[lr]::
5765::$$$message_0053_0014_0001$$$::The man in blue and the man in red.[lr]::
5766::$$$message_0053_0014_0002$$$::They looked human, but I know they're not.::
5767::$$$message_0053_0015_0000$$$::They could have been ghosts of some kind.[lr]::
5768::$$$message_0053_0015_0001$$$::But I've never heard of ghosts having forms that allow them to interact with humans like that.[lr]::
5769::$$$message_0053_0015_0002$$$::And the thing was talking, which makes it a little harder to believe it was a ghost, if it had a will of its own.[lr]::
5770::$$$message_0053_0015_0003$$$::From what I've heard, the only spirits that possess physical bodies are the elemental types, but I thought elementals didn't look human.::
5771::$$$message_0053_0016_0000$$$::"Well, that's not the issue here."[lr]::
5772::$$$message_0053_0016_0001$$$::There's a more fundamental issue.::
5773::$$$message_0053_0017_0000$$$::Those two were trying to kill each other.[lr]::
5774::$$$message_0053_0017_0001$$$::And there was a robbery and a murder at a house nearby.[lr]::
5775::$$$message_0053_0017_0002$$$::Eerie stuff like that has been plaguing Fuyuki lately.::
5776::$$$message_0053_0018_0000$$$::"..."[lr]::
5777::$$$message_0053_0018_0001$$$::With all of this in mind, the only conclusion I can come to is that the situation is out of my control.::
5778::$$$message_0053_0019_0000$$$::"If only the old man was alive right now..."[lr]::
5779::$$$message_0053_0019_0001$$$::I guess that was kind of whiny, but I'll put it down to the patched up chest wound that still feels so raw.::
5780::$$$message_0053_0020_0000$$$::"Idiot. I've already decided to do whatever I can...even if I don't understand what's going on."[lr]::
5781::$$$message_0053_0020_0001$$$::I can complain later.[lr]::
5782::$$$message_0053_0020_0002$$$::First of all, I need to decide whether I should get involved or not.[lr]::
5783::$$$message_0053_0020_0003$$$::"!?"::
5784::$$$message_0053_0021_0000$$$::The bell on the roof of the house rings.[lr]::
5785::$$$message_0053_0021_0001$$$::No matter what anyone says, this house is still a mage's house.[lr]::
5786::$$$message_0053_0021_0002$$$::A Bounded Field is set around it, and if there's ever an intruder in the area, an alarm rings.::
5787::$$$message_0053_0022_0000$$$::"A burglar at this hour?"[lr]::
5788::$$$message_0053_0022_0001$$$::I berate myself for my own idiocy.[lr]::
5789::$$$message_0053_0022_0002$$$::Of course it's not a burglar.::
5790::$$$message_0053_0023_0000$$$::Given the timing, right after that weird incident...[lr]::
5791::$$$message_0053_0023_0001$$$::There's definitely an intruder.[lr]::
5792::$$$message_0053_0023_0002$$$::It's no burglar. It's an assassin. They're here to take a life, not property.[lr]::
5793::$$$message_0053_0023_0003$$$::Because that man said so himself: [lr]::
5794::$$$message_0053_0023_0004$$$::[font italic=true]"You saw what you saw, so you gotta die."[font italic=false]::
5795::$$$message_0053_0024_0000$$$::"..."[lr]::
5796::$$$message_0053_0024_0001$$$::The house is dead silent.[lr]::
5797::$$$message_0053_0024_0002$$$::That same murderous intent I felt at school creeps closer through the hushed darkness.::
5798::$$$message_0053_0025_0000$$$::"...!"[lr]::
5799::$$$message_0053_0025_0001$$$::I gulp.[lr]::
5800::$$$message_0053_0025_0002$$$::A chill prickles like needles along my spine.[lr]::
5801::$$$message_0053_0025_0003$$$::It's no illusion and it's not my imagination... I know that the moment I leave this room, I'll be stabbed again.::
5802::$$$message_0053_0026_0000$$$::"...Nngh!"[lr]::
5803::$$$message_0053_0026_0001$$$::I desperately try to contain my scream.[lr]::
5804::$$$message_0053_0026_0002$$$::The instant I scream, the assassin will just leap right in and kill me.::
5805::$$$message_0053_0027_0000$$$::And that would just be a repeat of what happened before.[lr]::
5806::$$$message_0053_0027_0001$$$::I'm not prepared, and I'm going to be impaled again.::
5807::$$$message_0053_0028_0000$$$::"...Hnnn...haah...ghh..."[lr]::
5808::$$$message_0053_0028_0001$$$::My breathing grows labored as soon as that thought crosses my mind.[lr]::
5809::$$$message_0053_0028_0002$$$::I'm mad.[lr]::
5810::$$$message_0053_0028_0003$$$::I'm mad at myself for being afraid, and I'm mad that I've put myself in a situation where I'll so easily lose my life after it was saved earlier this same damn day.::
5811::$$$message_0053_0029_0000$$$::"...Ngh."[lr]::
5812::$$$message_0053_0029_0001$$$::I grit my teeth and hold my hand tight over my wounded chest to restrain myself.::
5813::$$$message_0053_0030_0000$$$::I need to get used to this.[lr]::
5814::$$$message_0053_0030_0001$$$::This is the second time.[lr]::
5815::$$$message_0053_0030_0002$$$::This is the second time I'm about to die.[lr]::
5816::$$$message_0053_0030_0003$$$::That alone motivates me not to die so pathetically as last time. Am I not a mage, after all?[lr]::
5817::$$$message_0053_0030_0004$$$::And if I can't even defend myself from this, what were my eight years of training for!?::
5818::$$$message_0053_0031_0000$$$::"Fine. Bring it on."[lr]::
5819::$$$message_0053_0031_0001$$$::I'm not going to agonize over complicated things anymore.[lr]::
5820::$$$message_0053_0031_0002$$$::Right now I just need to drive away whoever's here.::
5821::$$$message_0053_0032_0000$$$::"I need to find a weapon."[lr]::
5822::$$$message_0053_0032_0001$$$::I may call myself a mage, but the only thing I can do is reinforce something that might work as a weapon.[lr]::
5823::$$$message_0053_0032_0002$$$::You need a weapon to fight, after all.[lr]::
5824::$$$message_0053_0032_0003$$$::There's plenty of things that might work as a weapon in the storehouse, but I'm not anywhere near there.[lr]::
5825::$$$message_0053_0032_0004$$$::If I leave the living room and get ambushed, I'm just going to expose myself and it'll be a repeat of what happened earlier.::
5826::$$$message_0053_0033_0000$$$::It won't be easy, but I've got to find a weapon here.[lr]::
5827::$$$message_0053_0033_0001$$$::Something long and thin would be good. My opponent's weapon of choice is a spear, so a knife would be all but useless.[lr]::
5828::$$$message_0053_0033_0002$$$::A wooden sword would be best, but I obviously don't have one just lying around.[lr]::
5829::$$$message_0053_0033_0003$$$::Something around here that might be suitable as a weapon...::
5830::$$$message_0053_0034_0000$$$::"Whoa...there's only the poster Fuji-nee left..."[lr]::
5831::$$$message_0053_0034_0001$$$::I can't help but feel utterly dejected.[lr]::
5832::$$$message_0053_0034_0002$$$::But the desperation makes me all the more determined.[lr]::
5833::$$$message_0053_0034_0003$$$::The situation's so bad it can't really get any worse.[lr]::
5834::$$$message_0053_0034_0004$$$::Then all that's left for me to do is to move forward until I have no energy left.::
5835::$$$message_0053_0035_0000$$$::"Trace, on."[lr]::
5836::$$$message_0053_0035_0001$$$::I speak my incantation and I inject magical energy into the rolled-up, sixty centimeter poster.[lr]::
5837::$$$message_0053_0035_0002$$$::I try to imbue as much magical energy as I possibly can into the poster to solidify it, since it needs to work as a weapon to go up against that spear.::
5838::$$$message_0053_0036_0000$$$::"Composition, analyze."[lr]::
5839::$$$message_0053_0036_0001$$$::I focus my consciousness. [lr]::
5840::$$$message_0053_0036_0002$$$::Magical energy permeates the poster, as if I'm staining its fibers with my own blood.::
5841::$$$message_0053_0037_0000$$$::"Composition, reinforce."[lr]::
5842::$$$message_0053_0037_0001$$$::I feel that I've hit the end.[lr]::
5843::$$$message_0053_0037_0002$$$::Right before magical energy spreads throughout the poster and spills out, I say...[lr]::
5844::$$$message_0053_0037_0003$$$::"Trace, off."[lr]::
5845::$$$message_0053_0037_0004$$$::I cut off my connection with the poster. I tremble with excitement.::
5846::$$$message_0053_0038_0000$$$::The poster is hard as steel.[lr]::
5847::$$$message_0053_0038_0001$$$::But its weight remains the same as before. It's turned out great for a hastily improvised sword.::
5848::$$$message_0053_0039_0000$$$::"I...did it..."[lr]::
5849::$$$message_0053_0039_0001$$$::How long has it been since my Strengthening magecraft succeeded?[lr]::
5850::$$$message_0053_0039_0002$$$::My magecraft hasn't worked ever since Kiritsugu died, and so for it to succeed at a time like this seems ironic.::
5851::$$$message_0053_0040_0000$$$::"Either way, now I can..."[lr]::
5852::$$$message_0053_0040_0001$$$::I may be able to defend myself.[lr]::
5853::$$$message_0053_0040_0002$$$::I at least have some discipline in swordsmanship.[lr]::
5854::$$$message_0053_0040_0003$$$::I grip the poster with both hands and stand in the middle of the living room.::
5855::$$$message_0053_0041_0000$$$::If I stay here, I'm dead, but I don't think I can make it outside the mansion either.[lr]::
5856::$$$message_0053_0041_0001$$$::So I just need to head to the shed and make a stronger weapon there.::
5857::$$$message_0053_0042_0000$$$::"...Phew."[lr]::
5858::$$$message_0053_0042_0001$$$::Just as I start trying to hype myself up...[lr]::
5859::$$$message_0053_0042_0002$$$::"...!!!"[lr]::
5860::$$$message_0053_0042_0003$$$::Every hair on my body stands on end.::
5861::$$$message_0053_0043_0000$$$::I'm not sure when he got in.[lr]::
5862::$$$message_0053_0043_0001$$$::But the guy drops from the ceiling, straight toward me.::
5863::$$$message_0053_0044_0000$$$::"Wha...eh!?"[lr]::
5864::$$$message_0053_0044_0001$$$::A silvery flash strikes my head from above.[lr]::
5865::$$$message_0053_0044_0002$$$::I can only assume he came through the ceiling, and he descends on me, meaning to skewer my head.[lr]::
5866::$$$message_0053_0044_0003$$$::"Why...you!!!"[lr]::
5867::$$$message_0053_0044_0004$$$::I roll forward in a frantic dodge.::
5868::$$$message_0053_0045_0000$$$::The man lands with inhuman grace as I clumsily roll out of the way.[lr]::
5869::$$$message_0053_0045_0001$$$::I stop myself quickly and get to my feet, makeshift sword at the ready.::
5870::$$$message_0053_0046_0000$$$::[font italic=true]...[font italic=false][lr]::
5871::$$$message_0053_0046_0001$$$::The guy turns lazily, looking bored.::
5872::$$$message_0053_0047_0000$$$::"You're making this whole thing kind of a pain. I was trying to be nice, thinking it'd hurt a lot more if you saw me kill you."[lr]::
5873::$$$message_0053_0047_0001$$$::He shifts the spear to his other hand in a slow, fluid movement.::
5874::$$$message_0053_0048_0000$$$::[font italic=true]...[font italic=false][lr]::
5875::$$$message_0053_0048_0001$$$::I don't know why, but he doesn't seem as aggressive as he did at the school.[lr]::
5876::$$$message_0053_0048_0002$$$::Which...might give me a chance at escaping him.::
5877::$$$message_0053_0049_0000$$$::"I can't believe I have to kill the same human twice. Guess the living world is a meat grinder, no matter the era."[lr]::
5878::$$$message_0053_0049_0001$$$::He's...complaining to himself, like I'm not even here.::
5879::$$$message_0053_0050_0000$$$::[font italic=true]...[font italic=false][lr]::
5880::$$$message_0053_0050_0001$$$::I slowly retreat back out of the room.[lr]::
5881::$$$message_0053_0050_0002$$$::Only three more meters until I reach the window.[lr]::
5882::$$$message_0053_0050_0003$$$::I'll run out, then it's only about twenty meters to the shed once I reach the yard.[lr]::
5883::$$$message_0053_0050_0004$$$::Then I should quickly...::
5884::$$$message_0053_0051_0000$$$::"See ya. Don't wander around anymore, kid."[lr]::
5885::$$$message_0053_0051_0001$$$::He says it almost absentmindedly,[lr]::
5886::$$$message_0053_0051_0002$$$::like it was just an afterthought.::
5887::$$$message_0053_0052_0000$$$::"...Gah!"[lr]::
5888::$$$message_0053_0052_0001$$$::Pain shoots up my right arm.[lr]::
5889::$$$message_0053_0052_0002$$$::"...?"[lr]::
5890::$$$message_0053_0052_0003$$$::It all happens in an instant.[lr]::
5891::$$$message_0053_0052_0004$$$::He thrusts his spear forward, not even giving me time to react.::
5892::$$$message_0053_0053_0000$$$::I should've died for a second time right there.[lr]::
5893::$$$message_0053_0053_0001$$$::The makeshift sword in my hand spared me that fate.[lr]::
5894::$$$message_0053_0053_0002$$$::He probably thought I'd just been holding a rolled up paper.[lr]::
5895::$$$message_0053_0053_0003$$$::He struck as if I hadn't been holding anything at all, but the reinforced paper sword deflected the attack so it only grazed my arm.::
5896::$$$message_0053_0054_0000$$$::"Huh... Interesting trick you've got there, boy."[lr]::
5897::$$$message_0053_0054_0001$$$::His expression goes blank.[lr]::
5898::$$$message_0053_0054_0002$$$::His casual attitude from earlier vanishes entirely. He watches me now like a feral animal eyeing its prey.::
5899::$$$message_0053_0055_0000$$$::"...Ah..."[lr]::
5900::$$$message_0053_0055_0001$$$::Crap. I was clearly wrong, thinking things would be okay.[lr]::
5901::$$$message_0053_0055_0002$$$::This thing before me is some kind of demon, unbound by logic.[lr]::
5902::$$$message_0053_0055_0003$$$::I keenly realize that letting my guard down even for a second was beyond ludicrous.::
5903::$$$message_0053_0056_0000$$$::That's right.[lr]::
5904::$$$message_0053_0056_0001$$$::Desperate as things are, I should've just made a break for the window right after whatever miracle let me dodge his strike from above.::
5905::$$$message_0053_0057_0000$$$::"I thought you were just some kid, but I can sense a bit of magical energy from you. So that's how you're alive even after I stabbed you in the heart."[lr]::
5906::$$$message_0053_0057_0001$$$::The end of his spear points towards me.::
5907::$$$message_0053_0058_0000$$$::[font italic=true]...[font italic=false][lr]::
5908::$$$message_0053_0058_0001$$$::I can't block that.[lr]::
5909::$$$message_0053_0058_0002$$$::There's no way I'll be able to block that swift attack.[lr]::
5910::$$$message_0053_0058_0003$$$::I could've at least braced myself if he had a sword, no matter how fast he might be with it.[lr]::
5911::$$$message_0053_0058_0004$$$::But he's holding a spear.[lr]::
5912::$$$message_0053_0058_0005$$$::A sword is a whole line, but a spear is only a point.[lr]::
5913::$$$message_0053_0058_0006$$$::How am I supposed to block a point, when I can't even see how fast it moves?::
5914::$$$message_0053_0059_0000$$$::"Fine. I'm going to have a little fun."[lr]::
5915::$$$message_0053_0059_0001$$$::The man drops into a lower stance.[lr]::
5916::$$$message_0053_0059_0002$$$::In a flash...[lr]::
5917::$$$message_0053_0059_0003$$$::...the spear swings in sideways.::
5918::$$$message_0053_0060_0000$$$::I instinctively parry the blow aimed at my face.::
5919::$$$message_0053_0061_0000$$$::"Gngh...!?"[lr]::
5920::$$$message_0053_0061_0001$$$::"Good boy. Come on, here comes another."::
5921::$$$message_0053_0062_0000$$$::It's a [font italic=true]cyclone[font italic=false].[lr]::
5922::$$$message_0053_0062_0001$$$::I'm not sure how he's moving his spear in this small room, but it traces a beautiful arc without even touching the walls.[lr]::
5923::$$$message_0053_0062_0002$$$::"...Aaah!"[lr]::
5924::$$$message_0053_0062_0003$$$::The next swing comes from the opposite side, aiming at my torso.::
5925::$$$message_0053_0063_0000$$$::"Ga...agh!!!???"[lr]::
5926::$$$message_0053_0063_0001$$$::The force of the swing bends my makeshift sword as I try to parry.[lr]::
5927::$$$message_0053_0063_0002$$$::Monstrous...! Is that a hammer he's swinging!?[lr]::
5928::$$$message_0053_0063_0003$$$::Damn...the numbness in my arms is telling me that they might be broken!::
5929::$$$message_0053_0064_0000$$$::"Gh...why you!!!"[lr]::
5930::$$$message_0053_0064_0001$$$::"Hmmm?"[lr]::
5931::$$$message_0053_0064_0002$$$::I instinctively swing my sword.[lr]::
5932::$$$message_0053_0064_0003$$$::He must be mocking me with the way he keeps flicking his spear at my sword without drawing back at all.::
5933::$$$message_0053_0065_0000$$$::"Gngh...!"[lr]::
5934::$$$message_0053_0065_0001$$$::Numbness creeps into my arms after going on the attack.[lr]::
5935::$$$message_0053_0065_0002$$$::My makeshift sword bends even more, and the man's spear changes trajectory slightly.::
5936::$$$message_0053_0066_0000$$$::"You're hopeless. I gave you an opportunity but you wasted it. Then again, I guess expecting a good fight from a mage is asking too much."::
5937::$$$message_0053_0067_0000$$$::He moves like this is just a game.[lr]::
5938::$$$message_0053_0067_0001$$$::Such confidence... He'd been letting me take a swing at him after he took a couple shots at me.[lr]::
5939::$$$message_0053_0067_0002$$$::I wasted my one opportunity as nothing more than a stopgap.[lr]::
5940::$$$message_0053_0067_0003$$$::So he sees no point in continuing this.::
5941::$$$message_0053_0068_0000$$$::"What a disappointment you turned out to be. 'Kay, time to die, kid."[lr]::
5942::$$$message_0053_0068_0001$$$::The man readies his spear again.[lr]::
5943::$$$message_0053_0068_0002$$$::"Don't jump to conclusions!"[lr]::
5944::$$$message_0053_0068_0003$$$::During that microscopic opening...[lr]::
5945::$$$message_0053_0068_0004$$$::"Say what you want, dumbass!!!"[lr]::
5946::$$$message_0053_0068_0005$$$::I don't turn back to look; I just leap backward through the window.::
5947::$$$message_0053_0069_0000$$$::"Hnn...hnn..."[lr]::
5948::$$$message_0053_0069_0001$$$::My back shatters the window, and I roll out into the yard.[lr]::
5949::$$$message_0053_0069_0002$$$::I roll a few times, spring upward, and...[lr]::
5950::$$$message_0053_0069_0003$$$::"Ha...ah!"[lr]::
5951::$$$message_0053_0069_0004$$$::I blindly make my next move...[lr]::
5952::$$$message_0053_0069_0005$$$::I twist my entire body and swing behind myself!::
5953::$$$message_0053_0070_0000$$$::"Hmn!"[lr]::
5954::$$$message_0053_0070_0001$$$::I manage to bat the man's spear aside and he hesitates for just an instant.[lr]::
5955::$$$message_0053_0070_0002$$$::I knew it.[lr]::
5956::$$$message_0053_0070_0003$$$::If I jumped out the window, he was going to have to chase after me.[lr]::
5957::$$$message_0053_0070_0004$$$::And he would catch up to me and go in for the kill before I had the chance to get up.::
5958::$$$message_0053_0071_0000$$$::So I expected his fatal blow, and swung my sword to the side with all my might.[lr]::
5959::$$$message_0053_0071_0001$$$::It was a risky move. He'd have killed me if I'd been even a second late, and I'd have been just as dead if I was early too. But knowing the incredible gap in our skill, I figured there was no way I could've been early.::
5960::$$$message_0053_0072_0000$$$::The only thing I had to do was to get up as quickly as I could and parry the attack I knew would be coming at my back.[lr]::
5961::$$$message_0053_0072_0001$$$::The gamble pays off and my swing deflects his spear.::
5962::$$$message_0053_0073_0000$$$::"Ha...ah!"[lr]::
5963::$$$message_0053_0073_0001$$$::I quickly reposition myself.[lr]::
5964::$$$message_0053_0073_0002$$$::Now I just need to run to the shed while he's still confused...[lr]::
5965::$$$message_0053_0073_0003$$$::"Fly."::
5966::$$$message_0053_0074_0000$$$::"Huh?"[lr]::
5967::$$$message_0053_0074_0001$$$::He's not holding the spear anymore now, and he's right in front of me.[lr]::
5968::$$$message_0053_0074_0002$$$::He turns on the spot in a roundhouse kick.::
5969::$$$message_0053_0075_0000$$$::[font italic=true]...[font italic=false][lr]::
5970::$$$message_0053_0075_0001$$$::Scenery goes flying by.[lr]::
5971::$$$message_0053_0075_0002$$$::My chest goes numb where he kicked me. I can't breathe.[lr]::
5972::$$$message_0053_0075_0003$$$::The biggest surprise? I'm actually [font italic=true]flying[font italic=false] through the air.[lr]::
5973::$$$message_0053_0075_0004$$$::I never thought a guy kicking me would send me into the air like a damn ball.::
5974::$$$message_0053_0076_0000$$$::"Gngh!"[lr]::
5975::$$$message_0053_0076_0001$$$::I fall hard onto my back.[lr]::
5976::$$$message_0053_0076_0002$$$::I slam into a wall, the impact likely breaking my back, and slide down to the ground.::
5977::$$$message_0053_0077_0000$$$::"Ah...!"[lr]::
5978::$$$message_0053_0077_0001$$$::I can't breathe.[lr]::
5979::$$$message_0053_0077_0002$$$::My vision blurs.[lr]::
5980::$$$message_0053_0077_0003$$$::By a stroke of luck, he's thrown me into the shed I wanted to reach. I lean against the wall, trying to rouse myself.::
5981::$$$message_0053_0078_0000$$$::"Haah...haah..."[lr]::
5982::$$$message_0053_0078_0001$$$::I try to track the man through blurry eyes.[lr]::
5983::$$$message_0053_0078_0002$$$::He kicked me nearly twenty meters away.[lr]::
5984::$$$message_0053_0078_0003$$$::The guy picks his spear up and rushes straight at me.::
5985::$$$message_0053_0079_0000$$$::"Gngh!"[lr]::
5986::$$$message_0053_0079_0001$$$::I'm going to die.[lr]::
5987::$$$message_0053_0079_0002$$$::There's nothing I can do now.[lr]::
5988::$$$message_0053_0079_0003$$$::He's going to reach me.[lr]::
5989::$$$message_0053_0079_0004$$$::If I don't want to die, I need to get up and parry his...hit...::
5990::$$$message_0053_0080_0000$$$::[font italic=true]...[font italic=false][lr]::
5991::$$$message_0053_0080_0001$$$::The tip of the spear surges.[lr]::
5992::$$$message_0053_0080_0002$$$::I can't even look back at him. My body, on the verge of collapse, practically greets the spear.::
5993::$$$message_0053_0081_0000$$$::"Tch! Get on your feet, if you're a man!"[lr]::
5994::$$$message_0053_0081_0001$$$::What dumb luck.[lr]::
5995::$$$message_0053_0081_0002$$$::My knees give out; I can't hold myself up.[lr]::
5996::$$$message_0053_0081_0003$$$::The spear goes over my head and violently impales the shed's heavy door, pushing it open.::
5997::$$$message_0053_0082_0000$$$::"Ah..."[lr]::
5998::$$$message_0053_0082_0001$$$::And this is my last chance.[lr]::
5999::$$$message_0053_0082_0002$$$::If only I could get inside the shed, there should be something I can use as a weapon...!::
6000::$$$message_0053_0083_0000$$$::"Ungh...!"[lr]::
6001::$$$message_0053_0083_0001$$$::I crawl into the shed on all fours.[lr]::
6002::$$$message_0053_0083_0002$$$::Just then...[lr]::
6003::$$$message_0053_0083_0003$$$::"This ends now!"[lr]::
6004::$$$message_0053_0083_0004$$$::He launches the spear at me.::
6005::$$$message_0053_0084_0000$$$::"Daaaamn yooouuu!"[lr]::
6006::$$$message_0053_0084_0001$$$::I block it.[lr]::
6007::$$$message_0053_0084_0002$$$::I open up the rolled up poster to create a single-use shield.::
6008::$$$message_0053_0085_0000$$$::"Hm!?"[lr]::
6009::$$$message_0053_0085_0001$$$::The impact makes a dull sound.[lr]::
6010::$$$message_0053_0085_0002$$$::The poster, unrolled, probably isn't as strong.[lr]::
6011::$$$message_0053_0085_0003$$$::It blocks the spear, but it tears apart, returning to a normal bit of paper.::
6012::$$$message_0053_0086_0000$$$::"Ah...gngh!"[lr]::
6013::$$$message_0053_0086_0001$$$::The spear's impact flings me against the wall.::
6014::$$$message_0053_0087_0000$$$::"...Ah...zch...!"[lr]::
6015::$$$message_0053_0087_0001$$$::I fall on my butt, and try to get my heart beating again after it feels like it's trying to quit on me.[lr]::
6016::$$$message_0053_0087_0002$$$::The moment I raise my head to try to grab something to use as a weapon...[lr]::
6017::$$$message_0053_0087_0003$$$::"It's over. But that last move of yours surprised me, kid."[lr]::
6018::$$$message_0053_0087_0004$$$::The man points his spear in front of my face.::
6019::$$$message_0053_0088_0000$$$::"..."[lr]::
6020::$$$message_0053_0088_0001$$$::I can't do anything else now.[lr]::
6021::$$$message_0053_0088_0002$$$::His spear is pointed directly at my heart.[lr]::
6022::$$$message_0053_0088_0003$$$::I know this feeling.[lr]::
6023::$$$message_0053_0088_0004$$$::It's the scent of death, assailing my nostrils, reminding me of the pain I felt a few hours ago.::
6024::$$$message_0053_0089_0000$$$::"Honestly I don't get it. You're quick-witted but your magecraft's complete shit. You've got potential, but maybe you were just too young."::
6025::$$$message_0053_0090_0000$$$::I don't hear the man's voice.[lr]::
6026::$$$message_0053_0090_0001$$$::My attention is focused on the weapon pointed at me.[lr]::
6027::$$$message_0053_0090_0002$$$::Obviously.[lr]::
6028::$$$message_0053_0090_0003$$$::The moment he thrusts, I'm dead.[lr]::
6029::$$$message_0053_0090_0004$$$::What else is there to think of at this point?::
6030::$$$message_0053_0091_0000$$$::"I doubt it, but maybe you were the seventh one.[lr]::
6031::$$$message_0053_0091_0001$$$::Either way, this is the end for you."[lr]::
6032::$$$message_0053_0091_0002$$$::His arm jerks.[lr]::
6033::$$$message_0053_0091_0003$$$::I wasn't able to see his movements earlier, but now I see every last one in slow motion.::
6034::$$$message_0053_0092_0000$$$::There's a bolt of silvery light.[lr]::
6035::$$$message_0053_0092_0001$$$::The tip seems like it's being drawn towards my heart.[lr]::
6036::$$$message_0053_0092_0002$$$::Blood will gush from the wound in just a second...[lr]::
6037::$$$message_0053_0092_0003$$$::I know this feeling.[lr]::
6038::$$$message_0053_0092_0004$$$::That sensation of iron piercing my body.[lr]::
6039::$$$message_0053_0092_0005$$$::That taste of blood that will well up in my throat.[lr]::
6040::$$$message_0053_0092_0006$$$::That feeling of the world around me fading. [lr]::
6041::$$$message_0053_0092_0007$$$::I experienced all of it earlier today.[lr]::
6042::$$$message_0053_0092_0008$$$::And now I'm going to have to experience it again? Really?[lr]::
6043::$$$message_0053_0092_0009$$$::I don't understand. Why do I have to be the one who goes through this?::
6044::$$$message_0053_0093_0000$$$::This is bullshit.[lr]::
6045::$$$message_0053_0093_0001$$$:: No. I can't die in vain in a place like this.[lr]::
6046::$$$message_0053_0093_0002$$$::I was saved. If I was saved, I can't just die like this.[lr]::
6047::$$$message_0053_0093_0003$$$::I need to live to fulfill my obligations. I won't be able to do that if I'm dead.::
6048::$$$message_0053_0094_0000$$$::The spear is still going to impale me though.[lr]::
6049::$$$message_0053_0094_0001$$$::The tip will tear through my flesh, break my ribs, and bore into my heart.::
6050::$$$message_0053_0095_0000$$$::[font italic=true]...[font italic=false][lr]::
6051::$$$message_0053_0095_0001$$$::I'm mad.[lr]::
6052::$$$message_0053_0095_0002$$$::It shouldn't be so damn easy to kill people like this.[lr]::
6053::$$$message_0053_0095_0003$$$::I'm going to die, and it's bullshit.[lr]::
6054::$$$message_0053_0095_0004$$$::I'm going to die twice in a single goddamn day.[lr]::
6055::$$$message_0053_0095_0005$$$::[font italic=true]Everything[font italic=false] is fucking bullshit! I'm going to die and I didn't even have the opportunity to be [font italic=true]afraid[font italic=false] of this whole goddamn mess!::
6056::$$$message_0053_0096_0000$$$::"No way in hell! I...!"[lr]::
6057::$$$message_0053_0096_0001$$$::I'm not going to let myself...[lr]::
6058::$$$message_0053_0096_0002$$$::...die senselessly...[lr]::
6059::$$$message_0053_0096_0003$$$::...to the likes of YOU!!!!!!::
6060::$$$message_0053_0097_0000$$$::"Eh?"[lr]::
6061::$$$message_0053_0097_0001$$$::"Eh?" is absolutely the right word for this moment.[lr]::
6062::$$$message_0053_0097_0002$$$::"What...!?"[lr]::
6063::$$$message_0053_0097_0003$$$::Like magic...::
6064::$$$message_0053_0098_0000$$$::A figure appears out of a bright light shining from behind me.[lr]::
6065::$$$message_0053_0098_0001$$$::I can't think.[lr]::
6066::$$$message_0053_0098_0002$$$::All I know is that the figure is a girl.::
6067::$$$message_0053_0099_0000$$$::I hear a high-pitched sound.[lr]::
6068::$$$message_0053_0099_0001$$$::And the moment the figure appears, it pushes aside the spear pressed to my heart, and steps between me and the man without missing a beat.[lr]::
6069::$$$message_0053_0099_0002$$$::"Are you effin' [font italic=true]kidding me!?[font italic=false] The seventh Servant!?"[lr]::
6070::$$$message_0053_0099_0003$$$::He tries to regain his composure after his spear is pushed aside as the girl brandishes...[font italic=true]something[font italic=false] in her hand.::
6071::$$$message_0053_0100_0000$$$::Sparks fly.[lr]::
6072::$$$message_0053_0100_0001$$$::Hard metal clashes and sparks fly again.[lr]::
6073::$$$message_0053_0100_0002$$$::The man stomps his foot after blocking the woman's attack.[lr]::
6074::$$$message_0053_0100_0003$$$::"Kngh!"[lr]::
6075::$$$message_0053_0100_0004$$$::He must have realized he's at a disadvantage, because he leaps out of the storehouse with bestial agility.[lr]::
6076::$$$message_0053_0100_0005$$$::She must intimidate him, but she quietly turns towards me.::
6077::$$$message_0053_0101_0000$$$::The wind is strong today.[lr]::
6078::$$$message_0053_0101_0001$$$::The clouds slide away and the moon shines through for a brief instant.[lr]::
6079::$$$message_0053_0101_0002$$$::The silver moonlight shines into the shed, illuminating the girl, who appears like a knight.::
6080::$$$message_0053_0102_0000$$$::[font italic=true]...[font italic=false][lr]::
6081::$$$message_0053_0102_0001$$$::I'm speechless.[lr]::
6082::$$$message_0053_0102_0002$$$::And it's not because I'm confused by all the things that just happened.[lr]::
6083::$$$message_0053_0102_0003$$$::The girl before me is so astonishingly beautiful that I'm at a loss for words.::
6084::$$$message_0053_0103_0000$$$::[font italic=true]...[font italic=false][lr]::
6085::$$$message_0053_0103_0001$$$::The girl's eyes, like precious jewels, stare at me without emotion.[lr]::
6086::$$$message_0053_0103_0002$$$::"I ask of you, are you my Master?"[lr]::
6087::$$$message_0053_0103_0003$$$::Her voice sounds so...valiant.::
6088::$$$message_0053_0104_0000$$$::"Eh...Mas...ter?"[lr]::
6089::$$$message_0053_0104_0001$$$::I can only repeat her words back to her.[lr]::
6090::$$$message_0053_0104_0002$$$::I don't understand what she's saying, nor do I know who she is.[lr]::
6091::$$$message_0053_0104_0003$$$::All I know is that this slender, delicate-looking girl is similar to the man outside.::
6092::$$$message_0053_0105_0000$$$::"..."[lr]::
6093::$$$message_0053_0105_0001$$$::She says nothing, continuing to look at me in silence.[lr]::
6094::$$$message_0053_0105_0002$$$::I don't know how to describe her...[lr]::
6095::$$$message_0053_0105_0003$$$::She's...special. So special that I forget entirely about the man outside, even though he might attack at any moment.::
6096::$$$message_0053_0106_0000$$$::Time seems to have stopped.[lr]::
6097::$$$message_0053_0106_0001$$$::Even the fear of death I'd felt moments ago vanishes, and there is only the girl standing before me.::
6098::$$$message_0053_0107_0000$$$::"Servant, Saber. I have come in response to your summons.[lr]::
6099::$$$message_0053_0107_0001$$$::Master, please give me your orders."[lr]::
6100::$$$message_0053_0107_0002$$$::It's the second time she speaks.[lr]::
6101::$$$message_0053_0107_0003$$$::And the moment I hear the word "Master," and the name "Saber" echoes in my ears...::
6102::$$$message_0053_0108_0000$$$::"Ungh!"[lr]::
6103::$$$message_0053_0108_0001$$$::Pain shoots through my left hand.[lr]::
6104::$$$message_0053_0108_0002$$$::It's hot, like being branded by an iron.::
6105::$$$message_0053_0109_0000$$$::I unconsciously press the back of my left hand.[lr]::
6106::$$$message_0053_0109_0001$$$::Taking that as a sign, the girl silently nods her beautiful head.::
6107::$$$message_0053_0110_0000$$$::"Henceforth, my sword creates your destiny and our fates shall be intertwined.[lr]::
6108::$$$message_0053_0110_0001$$$::    And thus, our contract is formed."::
6109::$$$message_0053_0111_0000$$$::"Wha...contract? For what!?"[lr]::
6110::$$$message_0053_0111_0001$$$::I'm still a mage in training, so I understand what those words mean.[lr]::
6111::$$$message_0053_0111_0002$$$::But the girl doesn't respond to my question; she simply looks away with the same grace she'd shown when she nodded.::
6112::$$$message_0053_0112_0000$$$::She turns toward the shed's ruined door.[lr]::
6113::$$$message_0053_0112_0001$$$::Outside, the man readies his spear.::

